criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  First IVF cycle;

          -  With normal ovarian reserve(FSH < 10 mIU/mL; antral follicle count>5);

          -  With normal uterine.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pre-implantation genetic diagnosis cycles;

          -  Oocyte donation or sperm donation cycles.
